<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span style="color:#006d98">ش ح ح:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span style="color:#006d98">قوله تعالى:</span> <span style="color:#947721">{ومن يوق شح نفسه}</span> <span style="color:#707070">[الحشر: ٩]</span> أي بخل نفسه والشح:<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>